                            'Ballounes' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Ballounes' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which you burst coloured
balloons on a 10 by 10 tile board. The idea is to burst balloons where
there are at least one other balloon of the same colour next to the
balloon that burst, and the more balloons there are, the more points
you will get.

  Have fun!

